Package burlap.behavior.singleagent.vfa.common

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConcatenatedObjectFeatureVectorGenerator
    This class is used to produce a state feature vector that is the concatenation of the observable attributes of objects belonging to a specified sequence of object classes.
    FDFeatureVectorGenerator
    A wrapper for turning the features from a FeatureDatabase into a double array.
    FVToFeatureDatabase
    A class wrapper for converting a StateToFeatureVectorGenerator into a FeatureDatabase.
    LinearFVVFA
    This class can be used to perform linear value function approximation, either for a states or state-actions (Q-values).
    LinearVFA
    This class is used for general purpose linear VFA.
